## 

1. `./config.yaml`

   ```yaml
   user_info:
     username:
     password:
   
   step:
     minimum_steps: 26800
     max_steps: 29000
     steps: 8
   
   db_redis:
     host: 127.0.0.1
     port: 12308
     password: 0
     db: 0
   
   db_mysql:
     host: 127.0.0.1
     port: 12306
     user: root
     password: 0
     database: zeep_life
     charset: utf8mb4
   ```

   > `user_info`zeeplife
   >
   > `step``minimum_steps``max_steps``steps`
   >
   > `db_redis`redis
   >
   > `db_mysql`MySQL

   cd base
   C:\Users\chancey\AppData\Local\Programs\Python\Python36\python.exe startInit.py
